com.skratchdot.electribe.model.esx.presentation
Class EsxEditor

java.lang.Object
  MultiPageEditorPart
      com.skratchdot.electribe.model.esx.presentation.EsxEditor

public class EsxEditor
extends MultiPageEditorPart

This is the .esx model editor. It was initially generated by EMF. Also, initial tweaking was performed with the help of this article: http://www.eclipse.org/articles/article.php?file=Article-Integrating-EMF-GMF-Editors/index.html
